{
  "texts": [
    "IMPLEMENTATION A.",
    "Data Collection and PreparationData collection and preparation are critical for training the error correction model effectively.",
    "This subsection outlines the necessary steps to gather and prepare data:1) Identify Data Sources: Selection of diverse data sources that include a wide range of text types and errors typical in Chinese language processing, such as online forums, news articles, and literature.",
    "2) Data Acquisition: Secure agreements for data access and retrieve datasets using automated scraping tools or through direct dataset downloads.",
    "3) Data Cleaning: Perform initial data cleaning to remove irrelevant content, formatting errors, and non-textual elements to ensure data quality."
  ]
}